            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%233%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%A4%E8%86%9D%23&amp;extparam=%233%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%A4%E8%86%9D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#3个动作爬楼梯不伤膝#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%86%9D%E7%9B%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%86%9D%E7%9B%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#爬楼梯如何保护膝盖#</span></a>？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生建议：①身体保持直立，避免前倾；②膝盖弯曲尽可能小；③整个脚面着地，增加支撑力👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4982476733349923" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hl4uo3rwauj21hc0u0ack.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/j9uoPaZ6lx08bc2SouPS010412005Bpg0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1